{"tid":2247083,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕緣份計劃","createTime":"2020-10-17T14:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T18:50:02.000Z","uid":218575,"like":7,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6dd48abf5531a045eaf828c59934766592cf6b14","tid":2247083,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T14:21:01.000Z","msg":"聖誕緣份計劃 報名期至30/11/2015<br />\n<br />\n採用最佳科學方法配對<br />\n<br />\n為保障安全，本計劃不接受15歲女仔及16歲男仔參加。<br />\n<br />\n暫不接受hehe / sheshe<br />\n<br />\n不接受5P/MK呃蝦條，請自重。<br />\n<br />\n請注意安全，切勿隨意透露任何重要/個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提醒: 提議各位抱住識朋友的心態參與，以免做出奇怪行為/說話嚇怕對方。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">1. 填寫個人資料表格 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/x03RRL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2Fx03RRL&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=4af92fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/x03RRL</a><br />\n</span></span><br />\n2. 參加者資料 將於03/12公怖<br />\n<br />\n1.請不要透露自己的「個人配對編號」．否則取消資格。<br />\n<br />\n3. 提交「心儀對象排序表格」<br />\n<br />\n「心儀對象排序表格」會以電郵寄出．請查看電郵及垃圾郵件。<br />\n<br />\n1.排序對雙方保密，避免尷尬<br />\n<br />\n2.可選上限20個對象，請盡量不要漏空。<br />\n<br />\n3.結果以電郵通知，亦會同時收到對方電郵地址。<br />\n<br />\n4. 結果通知<br />\n<br />\n結果會以電郵通知。<br />\n<br />\n1. 配對結果只有一個。<br />\n任何因人為錯誤以致配對失敗，本人絕不負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請注意安全，切勿隨意透露任何重要/個人資料。"},{"pid":"1de59ab819d7d03105573b098e4ad2f757680984","tid":2247083,"uid":153781,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T14:22:01.000Z","msg":"g持 肥b出Pool<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d42ff08a0cb06912c64ea50934d2ab68e81080c","tid":2247083,"uid":361753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T14:22:06.000Z","msg":"係迷毒link 嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c7945b1a86b3cd7eca7af9b763371808764e89","tid":2247083,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"